Make a file named  10-monitor.conf in  (/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/) location.

and add copy the following to the created 10-monitor.conf file and save it.

Section "Monitor"

  Identifier "VGA1"
  Modeline "1920x1080" 138.500 1920 1968 2000 2080 1080 1083 1088 1111 +hsync -vsync
  Option "PreferredMode" "1920x1080"

Endsection
